long_description: Chocolate-coated Honey Stinger Protein bars provide big taste and 10g of protein. Use these protein bars as a great-tasting snack when you're on the go or to speed post-workout recovery. Protein bars are gluten free and contain no trans fats; each bar provides 22 vitamins and minerals, calcium and antioxidants. Nutrition facts displayed here and on wrapper may differ; information on wrapper reflects actual contents. *Discount will be applied when you check out; offer not valid for sale-price items ending in $._3 or $._9.
